      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies a key exchange using discrete logarithm cryptography that is authenticated using a password or passphrase.  It is resistant to active attack, passive attack, and offline dictionary attack.  This document is a product of the Crypto Forum Research Group (CFRG).&lt;/p&gt;</t>
